{"title":"Mondraker Summum DH Bike Packs MIND Suspension Telemetry System","link":"https://bikerumor.com/mondraker-summum-dh-bike-packs-mind-suspension-telemetry-system/","date":1683917100000,"content":"<p>The 2023 Mondraker Summum RR and R Downhill Bikes now benefit from the brand’s proprietary suspension telemetry system; <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mondraker-mind-integrated-telemetry-tool-perfects-easy-intuitive-suspension-setup/\" target=\"_blank\">MIND</a>. Designed to make suspension setup easier for the rider, no matter how much knowledge of mountain bike suspension they may or may not have, the system makes use of LEDs to help set the appropriate sag for their riding style. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then, during riding, it collects data on travel usage from the fork and shock, and subsequently presents that information in the MyMondraker App, where the rider can see how their suspension is performing, and make informed decisions on any adjustments necessary. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-fork-sensor-fender-integrated.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-fork-sensor-fender-integrated-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"mondraker mind telemetry fork travel sensor fender\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-fork-sensor-fender-integrated-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-fork-sensor-fender-integrated-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-fork-sensor-fender-integrated-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-fork-sensor-fender-integrated-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-fork-sensor-fender-integrated-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-fork-sensor-fender-integrated-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-fork-sensor-fender-integrated.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-telemetry-sensor-rocker-link.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-telemetry-sensor-rocker-link-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"mondraker mind telemetry rear wheel travel sensor\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-telemetry-sensor-rocker-link-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-telemetry-sensor-rocker-link-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-telemetry-sensor-rocker-link-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-telemetry-sensor-rocker-link-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-telemetry-sensor-rocker-link-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-telemetry-sensor-rocker-link-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-carbon-dh-bike-telemetry-sensor-rocker-link.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The MIND Telemetry System debuted on Mondraker’s <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mondraker-crafty-xr-ltd-bosch-performance-line-cx-race-motor/\" target=\"_blank\">Crafty eMTB</a> and <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2022-mondraker-foxy-carbon-goes-more-enduro-w-adjustable-geometry-and-stiffer-rear/\" target=\"_blank\">Foxy enduro bike</a> in 2021, but has since rolled it out to the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mondraker-super-foxy-goes-super-enduro-on-longer-travel-carbon-29er-trail-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">Super Foxy</a> super enduro bike, the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mondraker-raze-130mm-travel-do-it-all-trail-bike-is-mind-telemetry-equipped/\" target=\"_blank\">Raze trail bike</a>, and now the Mondraker Summum DH bike… with what looks to be actual availability with pricing given for the US, UK and Europe. Such integrated telemetry is unique to Mondraker, and the system cannot be retrofitted to any other bikes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-Summum-Carbon-R-mind-integrated-suspension-telemetry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"447\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-Summum-Carbon-R-mind-integrated-suspension-telemetry-800x447.jpg\" alt=\"2023 mondraker summum carbon r mind telemetry equipped dh bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-Summum-Carbon-R-mind-integrated-suspension-telemetry-800x447.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-Summum-Carbon-R-mind-integrated-suspension-telemetry-297x166.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-Summum-Carbon-R-mind-integrated-suspension-telemetry-120x67.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-Summum-Carbon-R-mind-integrated-suspension-telemetry-768x429.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-Summum-Carbon-R-mind-integrated-suspension-telemetry-1536x857.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-Summum-Carbon-R-mind-integrated-suspension-telemetry-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-Summum-Carbon-R-mind-integrated-suspension-telemetry.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Only the Carbon Summum Models are equipped with MIND Telemetry; this one is the more affordable of the two retailing at $9,499 USD</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>2023 Mondraker Summum RR &amp; R with MIND Telemetry</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Summum is Mondraker’s downhill bike, delivering 200mm of rear wheel travel through the ZERO Suspension platform. Therein, a solid rear triangle articulates about the front triangle via two links that co-rotate. These links mount the rear shock such that it is essentially floating, not directly connected to the front triangle. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike is piloted by the MS Mondraker Team on the World Cup Circuit, a roster that includes David Trummer, Eleonora Farina, Brook Macdonald, and Tuhoto Ariki.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Bike: 2023 Mondraker Summum Carbon RR &amp; R</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fork Travel: 203mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rear Wheel Travel: 200mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Wheel Size: MX – 29″ Front, 27.5″ Rear</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Pricing: $11,999 (RR), $ 9,499 (R)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-integrated-fork-fender.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-integrated-fork-fender-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"2023 mondraker summum mind telemetry fork travel sensor integrated with fender\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-integrated-fork-fender-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-integrated-fork-fender-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-integrated-fork-fender-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-integrated-fork-fender-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-integrated-fork-fender-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-integrated-fork-fender-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-integrated-fork-fender.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-rear-shock-sensor.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-rear-shock-sensor-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"2023 mondraker summum mind telemetry linkage sensor rear wheel travel\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-rear-shock-sensor-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-rear-shock-sensor-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-rear-shock-sensor-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-rear-shock-sensor-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-rear-shock-sensor-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-rear-shock-sensor-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/mondraker-summum-mind-telemetry-rear-shock-sensor.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For owners of the Carbon RR &amp; R Models, gone are the days of relying purely on ride feel to set up one’s suspension. The MIND Telemetry System, comprising a sensor integrated with the fork fender and steerer tube, and a sensor positioned on the rocker link, measures travel usage at 100 times per second. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It then transmits that data via Bluetooth to the MyMondraker App, where it is presented in a user-friendly graphical format, allowing the rider to make suspension setup decisions thereafter.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Key data collected include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Fork and Shock Travel Usage</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bottom-out events</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rider speed</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rider air time</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Travel usage upon take-off</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Travel usage upon landing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Maximum travel used</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-Mondraker-Summum-Carbon-RR-mind-telemetry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"443\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-Mondraker-Summum-Carbon-RR-mind-telemetry-800x443.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Mondraker Summum Carbon RR with MIND Telemetry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-Mondraker-Summum-Carbon-RR-mind-telemetry-800x443.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-Mondraker-Summum-Carbon-RR-mind-telemetry-297x164.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-Mondraker-Summum-Carbon-RR-mind-telemetry-120x66.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-Mondraker-Summum-Carbon-RR-mind-telemetry-768x425.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-Mondraker-Summum-Carbon-RR-mind-telemetry-1536x850.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-Mondraker-Summum-Carbon-RR-mind-telemetry.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Cream of the crop is the Summum RR, retailing at $11, 999 USD</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Only the Summum Carbon RR and Carbon R models come equipped with MIND. Both are offered in sizes Small, Medium, Large and XL, with reach figures of 430mm, 450mm, 475mm and 500mm, respectively. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Summum is designed around Mondraker’s so-call Forward Geometry principles, wherein a relatively long reach number is paired with a stem length adjustable between 25mm and 30mm. The latter is the Krypton DH stem, made by Mondraker’s own componentry brand, ONOFF.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-dh-geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"389\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-dh-geometry-800x389.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-dh-geometry-800x389.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-dh-geometry-297x144.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-dh-geometry-120x58.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-dh-geometry-768x373.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-dh-geometry-1536x747.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-mondraker-summum-dh-geometry.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>2023 Mondraker Summum geometry – click to enlarge</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><table><tbody><tr><td>2023 Mondraker</td><td>$ USD MSRP</td><td>£ GBP</td><td>€ GER/AUT/FRA/BENELUX</td><td>€ POR</td></tr><tr><td>Summum Carbon RR | MX</td><td>11,999</td><td>8,999</td><td>9,999</td><td>8,699</td></tr><tr><td>Summum Carbon R | MX</td><td>9,499</td><td>7,499</td><td>7,699</td><td>6,699</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Bike specification information can be found on the Mondraker website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://mondraker.com/\" target=\"_blank\">mondraker.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mondraker-summum-dh-bike-packs-mind-suspension-telemetry-system/\">Mondraker Summum DH Bike Packs MIND Suspension Telemetry System</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ccb3950620891ec9ae9a4315915dc575f121dfc0f3cd29466a93f93a42461aa7","category":"Cycling"}